Effect of bimekizumab on symptoms and impact of disease in patients with 
psoriatic arthritis over 3 years: results from BE ACTIVE.

Mease PJ(1), Asahina A(2), Gladman DD(3), Tanaka Y(4), Tillett W(5), Ink B(6), 
