A scoping review protocol on in vivo human plastic exposure and health impacts.

Goodes LM(1)(2), Wong EVS(1), Alex J(1), Mofflin L(1), Toshniwal P(1), Brunner 
M(1)(3), Solomons T(4), White E(1), Choudhury O(1), Seewoo BJ(1)(2), Mulders 
